    "Lastly, there will be a critical need to educate medical professionals to effectively collaborate with AI agents while maintaining full authority over the final clinical decision-making.",
    "Articlehttps://doi.org/10.1038/s43018-025-00991-6 Hematology and Medical Oncology.",
    "We retrieved and downloaded the relevant documents as either HTML extracted text or raw PDF files.",
